      "strategicPurpose": "",
      "iconName": "Contract:_Chase_Fate",
      "tips": "Aldous gains the ability to see the positions of enemy heroes for seconds. During this time, if Aldous uses this skill a second time while it is still in effect, then he permanently sees the position of one enemy hero. When Aldous hits that enemy hero, he will deal damage and cause knock back. Ending this ability early results in a decrease in cool-down time.",
